solar.role: Core processing engine; provides energy and synchronization to all nodes.

lunar.role: I/O balancer; regulates flow between external devices and internal glyphs.

spark.role: Computation surge node; handles transient operations and impulses.

stone.role: Foundation memory; stores persistent data and stabilizes runtime integrity.

daemon.role: System orchestrator; manages background processes and inter-link harmony.

tray.role: User interface bridge; exposes controls and runtime indicators.

hud.role: Visual layer; renders glyphs and world topology for the user.
